com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.reflection

Class CBClassTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.reflection.ClassTemplate<java.lang.Object>
      • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.reflection.CBClassTemplate

  • public class CBClassTemplate
extends ClassTemplate<java.lang.Object>
    A Class Template meant for pointing to a Class in the org.bukkit.craftbukkit Package
    Automatically deals with package versioning
    The empty constructor can be used to initialize this Class using the current Class name

    • Constructor Detail

      • CBClassTemplate

        protected CBClassTemplate()
        Initializes this CB Class Template using the CB Class name the same as this Class
        If this Class is called 'CraftServer', it will point to Class 'org.bukkit.craftbukkit.[version].CraftServer'
        A leading 'CB' or trailing 'Ref' is omitted from the Class name, avoiding the Class showing up in the imports

        This constructor should and can only be called by an extension of this Class
